{"tid":2347683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"周庭「升級」為甲類重犯，轉往大欖女懲教所單獨囚禁。","createTime":"2020-12-31T08:34:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T02:29:14.000Z","uid":361751,"like":4,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"7e162c235eb814baab26521173738b69438f61db","tid":2347683,"uid":361751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T08:34:50.000Z","msg":"消息指周庭現已被「升級」為甲類犯人（Cat A），轉往大欖女懲教所繼續服刑。<br />\n<br />\n前社福界立法會議員邵家臻指，甲類囚犯會被單獨囚禁及「重點看管」，在監獄內任何地方走動都會被兩名懲教人員「夾住」，其他還柙人士見狀要讓路。「衰啲講句，cat. A係就算屋企人有咩白事都唔使旨意有得出去。」<br />\n<br />\n【消息指周庭變「甲級犯」轉往大欖女懲教所服刑 邵家臻驚訝與謀殺同級】<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3aVwHut\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3aVwHut&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJm%2Bu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=2924c7d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3aVwHut</a><br />\n=============<br />\n📣 撐學生免費睇一年《蘋果》<br />\n學生申請：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/31gH84r\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F31gH84r&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJm%2Bu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=ff0ce5b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/31gH84r</a><br />\n=============<br />\n💪🏼 VIP撐《蘋果》計劃 每月$300起<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/30DSNv1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F30DSNv1&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJm%2Bu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=5808411e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/30DSNv1</a><br />\n=============<br />\n🍎 黎智英：經營非常困難 請支持訂閱<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2VLuV6g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2VLuV6g&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJm%2Bu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=d1e561c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2VLuV6g</a>"},{"pid":"6884697137cb8d3b7b92318c4506f9cbdaa96760","tid":2347683,"uid":361751,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T08:35:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7gsgDs4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7gsgDs4.png&h=e07b5b46&s={SIZE}